{"tid":2183433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台三地築人鏈 流亡手足撐港","createTime":"2020-09-01T02:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T05:59:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f305ca32eeaaa688eaa6a891cba3429e47dfcdc6","tid":2183433,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:44:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/Y74EH6C7HFCRZLBTSSTRM7DON4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FY74EH6C7HFCRZLBTSSTRM7DON4%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7p1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=55dc0a70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FY74EH6C7HFCRZLBTSSTRM7DON4%2F&h=0d9a999f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/Y74EH6C7HFCRZLBTSSTRM7DON4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台三地築人鏈 流亡手足撐港<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日是8.31太子站事件一周年，台北、台中及高雄昨同一時間有逾400人築起人鏈同寄哀思，當中據報包括流亡台灣的香港抗爭者。參加者亮起手機點點燈光，高舉「光時」黑底黃字標語，場面感人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台北<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kMcqzPZ05TIOHJQDh-s5WRomthI=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K6YM4KNSQ5EUBA4JSAYNGSIKOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkMcqzPZ05TIOHJQDh-s5WRomthI%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK6YM4KNSQ5EUBA4JSAYNGSIKOM.jpg&h=9e79d291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台北 ■台北昨晚舉行人鏈活動，眾人手持標語並亮起手機燈光聲援港人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促提供全面庇護<br />\n<br />\n台北人鏈活動以「手拖手 ! We Need You !」為口號，昨晚6時半在「保護傘」餐廳外舉行，主辦單位「周五護未來」用尼龍繩串起「Stand With Freedom」等旗幟，為港人在台北築起另一道連儂牆。活動晚上近8時估計有逾200人參加，人鏈近百公尺長。本身是台灣人的參加者小青（化名）昨手持自製的「手足被迫偷渡，需要政府庇護」標語參加台北人鏈活動。他向本報表示，五名被指計劃偷渡到台灣的香港抗爭者被台灣當局扣留，目前音訊全無，批評台灣政府承諾庇護港人，卻沒有明確的庇護機制，要求台灣落實人權保障，向香港求庇者提供全面庇護。<br />\n<br />\n同一時間，港人組織「維多利打狗」在高雄舉行人鏈活動，有150人參加，不少人穿全黑服裝、戴黃色頭盔出席，形成一條黑黃交錯的人鏈。有參加者披上「光時」旗幟，也有人手持「高雄撐香港」的白底黑字標語，在高雄寧靜街。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。當中不少是在台港人。Tracy說：「活動過程中也有請香港朋友們帶領我們一起喊口號跟唱《願榮光歸香港》，真的非常感動。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z94uXzfYp-DE1GimMrlV_1BOkXU=/1575x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HVLQI7WQ6JCBVFPNCNSG4ZYMAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz94uXzfYp-DE1GimMrlV_1BOkXU%3D%2F1575x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHVLQI7WQ6JCBVFPNCNSG4ZYMAQ.jpg&h=2012261b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■參加者用電子蠟燭砌出「831HK」，並擺放象徵抗爭運動的頭盔、眼罩及Pepe公仔。"},{"pid":"f4d4e72226b5a8345816970c8e3ad4d19849d077","tid":2183433,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce9c2c89a05362f73210026ea2f1a35a788e4ce","tid":2183433,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee278e7490532f77fca5b6e72d506140a288434","tid":2183433,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0270d60592b3fcf9e2aa4e63f2a0797ad70c6757","tid":2183433,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c047bbbc56056465e8302f6124c5ad4350cb61","tid":2183433,"uid":25558,